<body>
<div class="modify-content">
  <h1 class="title"><i class="fa fa-pencil"></i>輪播廣告設定</h1>
  <p class="modify-infr">可上傳檔案JPG / JPEG / GIF / PNG檔，尺寸限制1220*600px / 500kB以內。<br>本區最多可上6則廣告，您已設定4組，尚餘2組。</p>
  <div class="modify-form">
  	
	<div class="form-element edit-ad clearfix">
		<div class="edit-ad-preview">
			<span class="edit-ad-num">1</span><!-- ad num -->
			<div class="edit-ad-img"><img src="http://placehold.it/250x100/f1f1f1/666666"></div>
		</div>
		<dl class="edit-ad-content">
			<dd><label>請選擇上傳圖片</label><input type="file" accept="image/*"></dd>
			<dd><label>請設定圖片連結</label><input type="text" class="input-ad-url" placeholder="http://www.yoursite.com/yourpage.html"></dd>
			<dd><label>曝光時間</label><input type="text" class="input-ad-schedule" placeholder="請輸入開始時間" value="{default value}">~<input type="text" class="input-ad-schedule" placeholder="請輸入結束時間" value=""></dd>
		</dl>
		<button class="btn-clear-ad"><i class="fa fa-times"></i>清空廣告設定</button>
	</div>
	
